      "question_text": "2.53 g of  \\( NaHCO_{3}(s) \\)  was heated until no further changes and 1.59 g of a solid remained. Which of the following equations matches with the experimental result?\n\n(Relative atomic masses : H = 1.0, C = 12.0, O = 16.0, Na = 23.0)",
